Image Tweaks Module
by Jared Freed

Perform finishing touches on a provided computer or list of computers, these include:
- Set default applications
- Copy shortcuts and installers to node
- Add local policy to disable Firefox automatic update prompts

	load ps-img-tweaks
	
	     Option	 Required?			    Description
	[ host		|   Yes	  |	=> specify a single host or IP						]
	[ hostfile	|   No	  |	=> specify a file containing multiple hosts or IPs (one per line)	]
	[ proj		|   Yes	  |	=> specify a project (cfeec, opwdd, cyes, outreach)			]
	[ ffupdate	|   No	  |	=> should firefox update be disabled? (enable, disable)			]
	[ poisonedns    |   No    |     => resolve poisoned dns hostnames

